  description: Spacevoyage City is an incredibly diverse city where the headquarters
    of the Spacevoyage energy company is located. The superior technology allowed
    the city to remove most of the clouds and have perpetual sunshine in their city.
    However, this resulted in the rest of the planet being in almost perpetual darkness.
    Diversity and tolerance are the highest values in Spacevoyage City, however,
    only Spacevoyage employees are allowed to live in this city.
